definitions.definition: The language of the Faroe Islands , closely related to Icelandic , and more distantly to Danish, Norwegian, and Swedish.

main_definition: The language of the Faroe Islands , closely related to Icelandic , and more distantly to Danish, Norwegian, and Swedish.

definitions.definition: A person from the Faroe Islands ; a Faroe Islander .

main_definition: ( chiefly in the plural ) A person from the Faroe Islands ; a Faroe Islander .
